Johannes Gensfleisch zur Laden zum Gutenberg kɛ hɩɖɛ nɖɩ pɛsɛtaɣ tobi nɛ payaɣ size Gutenberg yɔ. Takayasɩ kɩbɩnzɩ taa lɛ, pama-ɖɩ fransɩ kʋnʋŋ taa sɩze Gutemberg. Ɖɔɖɔ lɛ, pama ɛ-hɩɖɛ kɩsɛsɛyɛ nɛ fransɩ taa size Jean. Gutemberg kɛ ɛjaɖɛ nɖɩ payaɣ-ɖɩ size Caama yɔ ɖɩ-tɛtʋ taa pɩɣa yaa ɖɩ-ɛjaɖɛ taa tʋ.

Palʋla-ɩ pɩnaɣ 1400 n̄ɩŋga taa kɛlɛ mbɩ yɔ. Egeetiye yaa tɛtʋ nɖɩ ɖɩ-taa palʋla-ɩ yɔ, nɖɩ payaɣ size Mayence  egeetiye. Ɖɩwɛ tɛtʋ ndʋ pɛcɛlɩ tʋʋ hɩɖɛ size ɖomu caama ampiiri kiɖeɖeu (Saint-Empire romain germanique) yɔ tɩ-taa. Ɛsɩba lɛlaɣ fenaɣ taa kɛ evemiye yaa kɩyakʋ naadozo n̄ɩŋgʋ wize kɛ pɩnaɣ 1468 n̄ɩŋga taa kɛ pɩnzɩ hiŋ loɖo lutozo taa.

[[File:Statue of Johannes Gutenberg on Place Gutenberg, Strasbourg.jpg|thumb|Statue of Ɖajaa Johannes Gutenberg, Place Gutenberg, Strasbourg tɛtʋ taa]]

Tɛtʋ sɔsɔtʋ ndʋ tɩ-taa paalʋla-ɩ yɔ, tɩ-taa ɖɔɖɔ ɛsɩba. ɛkɛ abalʋ tandaʋ tʋ nɔɔyʋ. Eyeba ɛ-tandaʋ ɛzɩ malɩŋ Ɛsɔ sɛyaa yekiɣ yɔ. Ɖajaa Johannes Gutenberg ɛnɛ, ɛkɛ taɣʋʋ tʋmɩyɛ tʋ yaa n̄ɩɣʋʋ tʋmɩyɛ laɖʋ sɔsɔ Caama tʋ weyi ɛ-hɩɖɛ sɛwa siŋŋ kɛ ɛ-ɛjaɖɛ taa nɛ kedeŋa kpeekpe yɔɔ yɔ.
Ɖajaa Caama tʋ ɛnɛ, ɛnʋ kɛna kajalaɣ yaa kɔɔnɔɔ tʋ weyi eluba yaa ɛlɩza mayaɣsɩ nzɩ palabazɩ nɛ n̄ɩɣlɩm yɔ. Sɩ-taa kɛlɛ hɔzɩŋ, nɛ malɩfanaa, nɛ pɩtasɩna ɖɔɖɔ masɩ kiciɣdasi. N̄ɩlɩm masɩ nzɩ, pɛkpɛndazɩ nɛ sɩwazɩ nɛ, patɩlɩ matʋ kɩmamatʋ.

