Ŋgʋ tovovnuŋ taa siŋŋ lɛ, elubutu yaa ɛlɩzɩtʋ kɛ pɩyʋ kem siŋŋ kɛ wɩsɩ ɖaɣnʋʋ naʋʋ nʋmɔʋ yaa hɔɔlʋʋ taa. Elubutu tasɩ sɔsʋʋ ɖoŋ lalaa lubutu nɛ pʋtʋlɩ nɔnɔɔ wendu kɩvatʋ lɛɣtʋ. Ɖɩtasɔɔ ɖɔɖɔ size, ɖajaa Jean Gutenberg luɖu ɛnɛ, ɛkata tɩlasɩ siŋŋ kɛ e-wezuu caɣʋʋ nʋmɔʋ taa.

Ɖajaa ɛnɛ, ɛna kʋn̄ɔŋ e-wezuu caɣʋʋ kpeekpe. Pɩtala alɩwaatʋ natʋyʋʋ lɛ, ɛcɔlɔ tʋ kpam ɖajaa Johann Fust lɛɣyaa e-nesi tɛɛ ɛ-tʋmɩyɛ wendu ndʋ ɛlakaɣna nɛ ɛtɔkɩ yɔ. Peeɖe ɛtɛza sʋʋ kʋn̄ɔŋ sɔsɔ kpeɖem.

[[File:Gutenberg Bible, Lenox Copy, New York Public Library, 2009. Pic 01.jpg|thumb|Ɖajaa Gutenberg tɛ Ɛsɔ Tɔm Takayaɣ, Lenox Copy, New York Public Library, 2009]]

Ɛ-kʋn̄ɔŋ ŋgʋʋ, kɩtana-ɩ ɛtɛ akpadayɩtʋ nɔɔ yɔ. Peeɖe ɖajaa sɩnɩyʋʋ sɔsɔ yaa ɛyaa pʋtɔdɩyɛ naʋʋ sɔsɔ Adolphe II de Nassau cɔnaɣ nɛ ɛkpa-ɩ nɛ ɛsɩ-ɩ ɛ-taɣyɔ yaa ɛ-ɖaɣ taa. Ɛha-ɩ hɩɖɛ kem size ɛyʋ kɩpanʋʋ nɛ ɛhɛyɩ akpadayɩtʋ liidiye nɛ pɩsɩɣna luɖu ɛnɛ nɛ, e-wezuu tasɩ wobinaʋ nɛ ɛsɩnda.

